ðŸ“˜ Konfigurasi DHCP Server dan DHCP Client di MikroTik
Konfigurasi Dasar Router A (Sebagai DHCP Server)
1. Setting IP Address
/ip address add address=192.0.0.2/24 interface="ke isp"
/ip address add address=192.168.1.1/24 interface=ether2
/ip address add address=192.168.2.1/24 interface=ether3
2. Setting Default Route (Gateway)
/ip route add dst-address=0.0.0.0/0 gateway=192.0.0.1
3. Setting DNS
/ip dns set servers=8.8.8.8,8.8.4.4 allow-remote-requests=yes
4. Setting Firewall NAT
/ip firewall nat add chain=srcnat out-interface="ke isp" action=masquerade
5. Tes Koneksi Internet
ping google.com
ðŸ“¡ Konfigurasi DHCP Server di Router A
GUI (Winbox/WebFig):
IP -> DHCP Server -> DHCP Setup
Langkah-langkah:
Klik tombol "DHCP Setup".
Pilih interface: ether3.
DHCP Address Space: 192.168.2.0/24 (otomatis).
Gateway: 192.168.2.1 (otomatis).
Address Pool: 192.168.2.2 - 192.168.2.254.
DNS Server: 8.8.8.8 (dari setting sebelumnya).
Lease Time: 1d.

ðŸ“¥ Konfigurasi DHCP Client di Router B
1. Mengganti Nama Router (Opsional)
/system identity set name="MikroTik B"
2. Setting DHCP Client
/ip dhcp-client add interface=ether1 use-peer-dns=yes use-peer-ntp=yes add-default-route=yes
3. Verifikasi IP Address
/ip address print
Cari entri dengan flag D (Dynamic) untuk melihat IP yang diperoleh dari DHCP Server Router A.
